})()","ai_justification":"Virtual Agent is the primary delivery channel for Now Assist conversational AI. Without glide.cs.enabled&#61;true, VA topics and Now Assist prompts cannot be surfaced to end users.","remediation_guidance":"Set glide.cs.enabled=true in sys_properties. Confirm the Virtual Agent plugin is active. Both must be true before Now Assist conversational AI topics can be surfaced to end users.","is_manual":"0","is_clone_sensitive":"0"},{"module":"ITSM","check_name":"Active VA Topic Count","order":"210","check_script":"(function(checkDef, dateFilter) {
